<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>١٧٣٠ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2956">أَبُو عَاصِمٍ، </a>عَنِ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/4035">ابْنِ جُرَيْجٍ، </a>عَنِ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/1448">الْحَسَنِ بْنِ مُسْلِمٍ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2980">طَاوُسٍ، </a>عَنِ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3732">ابْنِ عَبَّاسٍ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6225">مُعَاوِيَةَ </a><span class="special">﵃</span> قَالَ: <span class="c2">«قَصَّرْتُ عَنْ رَسُولِ اللهِ <span class="special">ﷺ</span> بِمِشْقَصٍ»</span>.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>